      "writtenOn": "2020-10-16T15:24:51Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "While I\u0027m thinking about this, I think the double-ternary equivalent for std::max(lo, std::min(x, hi)) is\n\n     return hi \u003c x ? hi\n          : lo \u003c x ? x\n          :          lo;\n\nJust like the existing double-ternary SkTPin() today, it\u0027s not particularly easy to rattle off my brain and fingers.",
