      "message": "Would it be a problem to change NaN to clamp to lo instead? \rDoes any of our code actually rely on the clamp-to-hi behavior intentionally?\n\nIt\u0027s common enough to pin to 0..1, in which case it might make more sense for NaN to fall to 0 anyway.",
